article_title: Next of kin sought for Charles Stokes, 34
article_text:
Next of kin sought (Photo: File)

The Jefferson County Coroner's Office is seeking next of kin for Charles Stokes, 34, of the 120 block of West Broadway. He died April 8.

If you have information on this person, please contact Deputy Coroner Rita Taylor at 502-574-6262.

Read or Share this story: http://cjky.it/1S30kc5
